Package com.github.jeuxjeux20.orderedmultibinders

Class OrderedMultibinders

java.lang.Object
com.github.jeuxjeux20.orderedmultibinders.OrderedMultibinders
public final class OrderedMultibinders
extends Object
Sorts elements of Modules' multibinders according to their @Order annotation.

Order ties

In case of an order tie (when the exact position of the element cannot be determined), the exact position is determined by:
  • their Order.position() value, which defaults to the given configuration's default position, note that it is applied even when the value is 0.
  • or their position in the multibinder set

Identifiers

Every binding's identifier (how they are referred to in @Order) is determined by the following:
Identifier for each type of binding
Type Result
UntargettedBinding Its key's type
InstanceBinding Its instance's class
ConstructorBinding Its constructor's declaring class
ConvertedConstantBinding Its value's class
ProviderKeyBinding Its provider key's type
ProviderInstanceBinding Its provider instance's class
LinkedKeyBinding Its linked key's type
If multiple bindings have the same identifier, a DuplicateIdentifiersException is thrown.
